<title>SPAIN: SOCCER-LOGRONES COACH BANS MOBILE PHONES.</title>
<headline>SOCCER-LOGRONES COACH BANS MOBILE PHONES.</headline>
<dateline>MADRID 1996-11-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Struggling Spanish first division side Logrones have found a scapegoat for their run of defeats -- the mobile phone.</p>
<p>Coach Liber Arispe has banned the use of portable phones in Las Gaunas stadium, during training and while travelling to away games after several pre-match talks were interrupted by calls to players.</p>
